OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776438666
OL,3,CFirst charges brought against ICE
OL,4,Cagent involved in US immigration
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,FCriminal charges have been brought for
OL,8,Fthe first time against a federal
OL,9,Fofficer involved in the controversial
OL,10,Fimmigration crackdown in the US state
OL,11,Fof Minnesota.
OL,13,FThe Immigration and Customs
OL,14,FEnforcement (ICE) agent has been
OL,15,Faccused of pointing his gun at the
OL,16,Foccupants of a car, after pulling
OL,17,Falongside them on a Minneapolis-area
OL,18,Fhighway.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776438666
OL,3,CFirst charges brought against ICE
OL,4,Cagent involved in US immigration
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,FGregory Donnell Morgan Jr. is charged
OL,8,Fwith two counts of second-degree
OL,9,Fassault, Minnesota prosecutors said on
OL,10,FThursday.
OL,12,FHennepin County Attorney Mary Moriarty
OL,13,Fsaid this the first criminal case
OL,14,Fagainst an officer involved in the ICE
OL,15,Fcrackdown, which was part of a surge
OL,16,Fof forces into cities including Los
OL,17,FAngeles, Chicago and New Orleans.
OL,19,FThe crackdown by the Trump
OL,20,Fadministration has been hugely
OL,21,Fcontroversial.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776438666
OL,3,CFirst charges brought against ICE
OL,4,Cagent involved in US immigration
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,FAbout 3,000 federal officers were
OL,8,Fdeployed to the Minneapolis-St. Paul
OL,9,Farea from December through February in
OL,10,Fwhat the department called its
OL,11,F"largest immigration enforcement
OL,12,Foperation ever."
OL,14,FThe Minnesota operation led to
OL,15,Fthousands of arrests, angry mass
OL,16,Fprotests and the fatal shootings of
OL,17,Ftwo US citizens.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776438666
OL,3,CFirst charges brought against ICE
OL,4,Cagent involved in US immigration
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,FThe deaths were hugely divisive, with
OL,8,FTrump supporters claiming the
OL,9,Fprotesters should not have got in the
OL,10,Fway of the officers, while Trump's
OL,11,Fopponents said their actions were a
OL,12,Fhuge overreach of federal power and
OL,13,Fwere an excessive use of force.
OL,15,F"There is no such thing as absolute
OL,16,Fimmunity for federal agents who
OL,17,Fviolate the law in the state of
OL,18,FMinnesota," Moriarty told a news
OL,19,Fconference, saying the agent acted
OL,20,Foutside the scope of a federal
OL,21,Fofficer's authority.
OL,26,@wD@AOUzD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776438666
OL,3,CFirst charges brought against ICE
OL,4,Cagent involved in US immigration
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,FMinnesota authorities say Morgan, 35,
OL,8,Fwas driving back to immigration
OL,9,Foffices at the end of his shift when
OL,10,Fthe incident occurred on February 5.
OL,12,FThe driver and front-seat passenger of
OL,13,Fa car called 911, saying the driver of
OL,14,Fan unmarked SUV pulled alongside them,
OL,15,Frolled down his window and pointed a
OL,16,Fhandgun at them both.
OL,18,FThe car's driver told investigators
OL,19,Fthey feared it was a "crazy person
OL,20,Fdriving down the road aiming guns at
OL,21,Fpeople," according to the warrant.
OL,26,@{D@VOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776438666
OL,3,CFirst charges brought against ICE
OL,4,Cagent involved in US immigration
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,FA spokesman for Moriarty's office said
OL,8,Fno arrangements have been made for
OL,9,FMorgan to surrender and that there is
OL,10,Fan active nationwide warrant for his
OL,11,Farrest.
OL,13,FIf convicted, Morgan faces up to seven
OL,14,Fyears in prison for each assault
OL,15,Fcharge.
OL,17,FMorgan, the Department of Homeland
OL,18,FSecurity and the Justice Department
OL,19,Fhave not yet commented on the case.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776438666
OL,3,CFirst charges brought against ICE
OL,4,Cagent involved in US immigration
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,FMoriarty said during a news conference
OL,8,Fthat Morgan was driving a rented,
OL,9,Funmarked SUV on the shoulder of the
OL,10,Fhighway when a car also moved into the
OL,11,Fshoulder to try to slow Morgan down,
OL,12,Fits driver not knowing he was an
OL,13,Fofficer.
OL,15,FAfter the car returned to the legal
OL,16,Flane, she said, Morgan pulled up
OL,17,Falongside and pointed his service
OL,18,Fweapon at the two people in the car.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31008
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776438666
OL,3,CFirst charges brought against ICE
OL,4,Cagent involved in US immigration
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,FAccording to the warrant, Morgan then
OL,8,Fmerged his SUV back into traffic ahead
OL,9,Fof the victims, who took cellphone
OL,10,Fphotos of the SUV's license plate.
OL,12,FThe warrant does not identify the
OL,13,Fvictims.
OL,15,FMorgan and his partner, who was not
OL,16,Fcharged, told investigators they were
OL,17,Freturning at the end of their shift to
OL,18,Fthe federal building being used to
OL,19,Fstage officers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
