FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31009
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776438666
OL,3,CFirst charges brought against ICE
OL,4,Cagent involved in US immigration
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,FThe arrest warrant says Morgan "made
OL,8,Fno claim that he was conducting any
OL,9,Flaw-enforcement operation or activity
OL,10,For responding to any emergency
OL,11,Fsituation."
OL,13,FMorgan told investigators with the
OL,14,FMinnesota State Patrol that the other
OL,15,Fvehicle "swerved over in front of him
OL,16,Fand cut him off," the warrant said.
OL,18,FInvestigators wrote that Morgan said
OL,19,F"he feared for his safety and the
OL,20,Fsafety of others" when he drew his gun
OL,21,Fand yelled: "Police! Stop!"
