OL,3,CFirst charges brought against ICE
OL,4,Cagent involved in US immigration
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,FThe warrant says the victims couldn't
OL,8,Ftell Morgan was a law enforcement
OL,9,Fofficer and couldn't hear him because
OL,10,Ftheir windows were up.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FThe charges could intensify a clash
OL,18,Fbetween the Trump administration and
OL,19,FMinnesota officials over the crackdown.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
