OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776438666
OL,3,CFirst charges brought against ICE
OL,4,Cagent involved in US immigration
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,FTodd Blanche, the acting attorney
OL,8,Fgeneral, has warned that the Justice
OL,9,FDepartment could investigate and
OL,10,Fprosecute state or local officials who
OL,11,Farrest federal agents for performing
OL,12,Ftheir official duties.
OL,14,FMoriarty said she is not concerned
OL,15,Fabout blowback from federal
OL,16,Fauthorities and that her office will
OL,17,F"hold people accountable if they
OL,18,Fviolate the laws of the state."
OL,26,@yD@AOUzD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
