OL,3,CFirst charges brought against ICE
OL,4,Cagent involved in US immigration
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,FMinnesota authorities continue to
OL,8,Finvestigate the conduct of federal
OL,9,Fofficers during the immigration
OL,10,Fcrackdown, insisting they can't trust
OL,11,Fthe federal government to investigate
OL,12,Fitself.
OL,14,FMinnesota sued the Trump
OL,15,Fadministration last month for access
OL,16,Fto evidence in three cases involving
OL,17,Fshootings by federal officers,
OL,18,Fincluding the killings of Renee Good
OL,19,Fand Alex Pretti.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
